flowchart TD
  Handler[Controller handler returns data] --> Interceptor[ApiResponseInterceptor]
  Interceptor --> Check{CursorPaginationResult?}
  Check -->|yes| Paginated[Envelope data array and pagination meta]
  Check -->|no| Plain[Envelope data and empty meta]
  Paginated --> Success[success true message data meta]
  Plain --> Success
  Success --> Client[Client]

  Handler -. throws .-> Filter[HttpExceptionFilter]
  Filter --> App{AppException?}
  App -->|yes| AppError[Use explicit ErrorCodes value]
  App -->|no HttpException| HttpError[Use validation or exception name]
  App -->|unknown| Unknown[INTERNAL_SERVER_ERROR]
  AppError --> ErrorResponse[success false error code message]
  HttpError --> ErrorResponse
  Unknown --> ErrorResponse
  ErrorResponse --> Client
